            ; he does not live there himself, nor any of his servants. On Saturday the 19th of June I lost two watches, two breast buckles, a tea spoon, and a handkerchief. I came home and found my door open. It was shut and locked when I went out.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18130714-25-person341">
                  ALEXANDER 
                  BALL
