            . I searched the prisoner first and then I searched his lodgings. By his bed I found a silver spoon marked P D. I found two breast buckles, the duplicate of a watch, and a gold ring.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18130714-25-person342">
                  EDWARD 
                  CLARK
